# The Flutter scaffold is generated by CI (flutter create) and then overlaid
# with arcore_src/. Committing it would mean carrying Gradle wrappers and
# platform boilerplate that the build regenerates anyway.
#
# SOURCE OF TRUTH IS arcore_src/ — edit there, never in the generated tree.
